The '''Hartford Hawks''' are the athletic teams of the [[University of Hartford]]. The school sponsors 18 varsity sports (9 men's, 9 women's), all of which compete in the [[Division I (NCAA)|Division I]] [[America East Conference]]. The Hawks' colors are scarlet and white.
